	<p style="margin: 9.75pt 0cm;"><strong>Teacher&rsquo;s Editions</strong><strong></strong></p>
<p>The Teacher's Edition features page-by-page wraparound commentary overlaid on the actual pages of the original student text. Advice and practical ideas are provided to help teachers implement the new curriculum, including the cross-curricular capabilities. The book includes answers, extension ideas for more capable students and tips for assessment.</p>
